                          Make sure it's set to static
                          
                          IP Address: 208.8.8.200
                          Subnet Mask: 255.255.255.0
                          Default Gateway: 208.8.8.2
                          Preferred DNS Server: 127.0.0.1

                          Click "Advanced"
